    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone seeking a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are sound, and it starts up without issue every time. However, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood. The interior is clean but exhibits visible wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It has been regularly maintained, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
