      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new ride that\u2019s ready for all your adventures? I\u2019m selling my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really solid shape! It has been well-loved and taken care of, so it\u2019s running beautifully and looking great. It's the perfect blend of comfort and dependability, whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come by and take it for a test drive\u2014I think you\u2019ll really enjoy how it feels on the road!",
      "price": 31500.0,
